        <p class="text-sm text-tjb-charcoal">Medicaid doula coverage is evolving quickly. States frequently update their reimbursement rates, covered visit limits, and provider qualification requirements. Always verify current coverage with your state's Medicaid agency or your managed care plan before hiring a doula. The information above reflects policies in effect as of early 2026 but may have changed since publication.</p>
